  "detailed_description": "Legend of the Skyfish is a beautiful level-based adventure puzzler with a unique weapon and tool - a fishing pole!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFollow the intrepid Little Red Hook on her journey with the Moonwhale to defeat the monstrous Skyfish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your fishing pole as a weapon or a grappling hook, and upgrade it as you go.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLegend of the Skyfish is filled with beautiful hand-painted art, intricate action puzzles and unique enemies. Explore a huge world of 45 handcrafted levels and defeat giant bosses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Unique fishing/grappling hook mechanics<br />\r\n- Gorgeous hand-painted environments and creatures<br />\r\n- Original music score by Sean Beeson<br />\r\n- 45 handcrafted levels<br />\r\n- Epic boss fights<br />\r\n- Many items to find and use <br />\r\n- Various puzzles to solve<br />\r\n- Great for all ages!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd also:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Controller Support",
  "about_the_game": "Legend of the Skyfish is a beautiful level-based adventure puzzler with a unique weapon and tool - a fishing pole!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFollow the intrepid Little Red Hook on her journey with the Moonwhale to defeat the monstrous Skyfish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your fishing pole as a weapon or a grappling hook, and upgrade it as you go.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLegend of the Skyfish is filled with beautiful hand-painted art, intricate action puzzles and unique enemies. Explore a huge world of 45 handcrafted levels and defeat giant bosses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Unique fishing/grappling hook mechanics<br />\r\n- Gorgeous hand-painted environments and creatures<br />\r\n- Original music score by Sean Beeson<br />\r\n- 45 handcrafted levels<br />\r\n- Epic boss fights<br />\r\n- Many items to find and use <br />\r\n- Various puzzles to solve<br />\r\n- Great for all ages!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd also:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Controller Support",
